viper's bugloss
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:also (mistakenly and locally) called blue borage, a weed with blue flowers found along roadsides, in riverbeds and other dry places. =BLUE WEED, =BLUE BORAGE
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
